name: Greetings!
bio: I am Jessica Figueroa, a Fullstack Software Engineer. Recently, I graduated from the Software Engineering Immersive at General Assembly in June of 2023. With a strong foundation in many programming languages, web development, and a customer-centric mindset, I'm eager to contribute my problem-solving skills and passion for technology to create innovative solutions. My areas of expertise are with React.js and Python.
